    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的主人公是一名专业咖啡师，在一次偶然的机会中被迫成为一名调酒师。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助他在这门手艺上取得成功！参观各种场所，学习新配方，结识业内人士并学习他们的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/extras/ea680a1302288c160461a874d179a1bd.poster.avif?t=1762609631\" width=800 height=289 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/extras/ea680a1302288c160461a874d179a1bd.webm?t=1762609631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有你的技能才能决定你能否成功地调制出各种鸡尾酒并准时上桌。你能应付高速运转的工作吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游戏的混乱性质，建立自己的战术。使用提示或设计自己的策略，以最少的移动和互动快速送达订单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/extras/d3c7da37a94c0e9e187089187fd585fe.poster.avif?t=1762609631\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/extras/d3c7da37a94c0e9e187089187fd585fe.webm?t=1762609631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >速度越快越好，但也不能忘记保证质量。毕竟，错误的成分只会制造出垃圾。客户越满意，反馈就越好，你就能得到更多的星星。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有您的行动才能决定故事的结局！</p>",
